                        <div id="hs_cos_wrapper_intro_text" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module widget-type-rich_text widget-type-rich_text" style="color: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module"><div id="hs_cos_wrapper_intro_text_" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="color: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin: 0 0 30px 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; font-family: 'Satoshi', 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Big March. AI agents now can reach across connected tools and get things done. Templates make documentation standards automatic. Saved views publish once and show up everywhere they should. Six features live today. Here is the rundown.⚡</p></div></div>
                        
                        <!-- TL;DR Section -->
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin: 30px 0 20px 0; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Satoshi', 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">📌 TL;DR</p>
                        
