                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin: 30px 0 20px 0; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Satoshi', 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">🎉 New Features</p>
                        
                        <!-- Feature 1: MCP Server Connector -->
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin: 0 0 5px 0; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 'Satoshi', 'Montserrat', sans-serif;"><strong style="color: #A0DDFD; border-left: 3px solid #A0DDFD; padding-left: 8px;">MCP Server Connector</strong></p>
                        
                        <div id="hs_cos_wrapper_feature_1_description" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module widget-type-rich_text" style="color: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module"><div id="hs_cos_wrapper_feature_1_description_" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="color: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 'Satoshi', 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Connect Transform to any application with an MCP server. Use account-level connections for internal tools: ERP, CRM, PSA, or chat platforms like Slack or Teams. Use org-level connections to work directly with customer systems. Authenticate once, then describe the outcome. Transform chains the tool calls together and gets it done.</p></div></div>
                        
