                        <div id="hs_cos_wrapper_feature_4_description" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module widget-type-rich_text" style="color: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module"><div id="hs_cos_wrapper_feature_4_description_" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="color: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 'Satoshi', 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Point a pivot table at any saved view and the data updates automatically as the view does. Swap between sprint views without rebuilding anything. Need a one-off cut? Create a custom filter directly on the pivot instead.</p></div></div>
                        
